>or just Eroge Anthro game recomendations
One to keep an eye on is Wild Life. It's a project started by a couple of German dudes that grew into a full-blown game studio over the years. It is still very much unfinished, but they're finally starting up proper production of the final assets for the full release, which is still a few years out. When done, it will be a 3D action-adventure game with NPCs (both human and anthro) you can fuck. Time will tell if the gameplay will be any good (currently it's pretty raw and basic), but the sex animations are already shaping up to be quite nice, unsurprisingly so as one of the original founders is an animator.

Recently, they improved the sandbox mode of their WIP Patreon builds (which previously could only handle one sex scene at a time) with extended editing capabilities, essentially turning it into a level editor. It even has scripting capabilities for those who really want to sink their teeth into it. Pic related is an example of what can be done with it without using any of the more special features. It does have the limitation of only supporting characters, poses and animations shipped with the game, but who knows, in the future I'd say at least custom poses might be in the cards.
